---
title: Baked Thai Red Chicken & Chickpea Curry with Rapid Rice & Peanuts
description: Enjoy a bowl of rich and creamy Thai red curry, loaded with tender chicken, colourful veggies, wholesome chickpeas and aromatic spices. With a
sprinkling of roasted peanuts to finish it all off, this delicious meal will beat your local takeaway joint!
